{"tid":1053801,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母 香港LG","createTime":"2019-03-09T11:02:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T14:06:52.000Z","uid":84050,"like":127,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"5a81a47e636f4b5e80e9c56e41db339a287576e1","tid":1053801,"uid":84050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:02:07.000Z","msg":"本人用左LG 差唔多7年<br />\n由G pro ,G4 ,G5 用到V20<br />\n雖然LG 一向比人屌佢7 燒底版<br />\n但我都一直都好鐘意用<br />\n因為覺得佢有得換電 始終係賣點<br />\n同埋我係用V20 ,加舊淘仔8000mAh 電真係可以狂用一日唔洗差電 升左8.0夠快, 影相Ok, 聲靚, 其實我真心想一直用我部V20 用到5G 普及先買新機<br />\n<br />\n到最近保養期就完 諗住係唔係都去代理check 下 修理下<br />\n仆佢個臭街 <br />\n點知話我部機液體損壞<br />\n如果要整要36xx <br />\n我緊係唔撚濟 <br />\n跟住佢話好 但點都要比$150 檢查費<br />\n我屌佢老味 咁你保養期夠竟包咩?<br />\n都算 到比左$150<br />\n拿機果時 掛住屌7佢 無check到部機<br />\n點知一番到屋企 開番部機時<br />\n部機已經只係開到 但觸控完全用唔到<br />\n試左幾次都唔得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母香港LG<br />\n你依家要我比$150 仲要整撚壞埋我部機<br />\n真心好撚嬲 點解你可以做到自己咁撚7<br />\n死仆街 LG永不錄用<br />\n(就算用都買水貨算 無咁撚慶)"},{"pid":"4a0690e3f38769c882ad8121bc2d5aee57e2ea6f","tid":1053801,"uid":89514,"like":5,"dislike":60,"score":-55,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:07:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8092223db71ebd7878d86958fa3d117f2e6bdff0","tid":1053801,"uid":84050,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4a0690e3f38769c882ad8121bc2d5aee57e2ea6f","tid":1053801,"uid":89514,"like":5,"dislike":60,"score":-55,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:07:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:11:34.000Z","msg":"香港LG 咁樣搞7 自己d 機 就算用既都係買水貨算"},{"pid":"05bf4ffb222df4ef7cdbd618ffa1293c0b33ad7d","tid":1053801,"uid":43966,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"4a0690e3f38769c882ad8121bc2d5aee57e2ea6f","tid":1053801,"uid":89514,"like":5,"dislike":60,"score":-55,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:07:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:14:43.000Z","msg":"用撚過一次g3 永不錄用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n果陣買部g3 用左個零月 後面lock制唔識回彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我拎上旺角客服 佢死話無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死都唔同我換<br />\n我叫佢拎同一款機出黎對比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢死都唔制<br />\n好似我思覺失調好撚得閒咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母啦香港LG. <br />\n唔撚會再買你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc337556d491d30787a0a7d13dd26ebcfa94d0c","tid":1053801,"uid":89514,"like":4,"dislike":34,"score":-30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:15:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d46e033b960693d7561613c034b9f07f7c82fb14","tid":1053801,"uid":43369,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:16:42.000Z","msg":"v30 用左1年 上去換左2 次mon都好爽手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家過檔三叔"},{"pid":"fcbd5a8cb90f04afe99f9e838494fb0fbf76051d","tid":1053801,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:21:42.000Z","msg":"無野無啦啦拎咩去整? 打手?"},{"pid":"182498cac6fd96a7b2e03030bd83091e7fb0df14","tid":1053801,"uid":38456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:22:04.000Z","msg":"單呢"},{"pid":"b84de047d2a30770016b01f8fa9b668924330689","tid":1053801,"uid":163291,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"4a0690e3f38769c882ad8121bc2d5aee57e2ea6f","tid":1053801,"uid":89514,"like":5,"dislike":60,"score":-55,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:07:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:24:02.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 人曲線你曲得咁柒 idog狗"},{"pid":"2125c07adc2b83829e2bd20d7cb8b7c4b4b426d5","tid":1053801,"uid":215111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T11:24:12.000Z","msg":"無圖無真相"},{"pid":"86b5f8f1baea20f461a2f2e823144f626698ef91","tid":105380